Paper: 09041936
Title: Fermions in (Anti) de Sitter Gravity in Four Dimensions
Authors: Noriaki Ikeda and Takeshi Fukuyama
Abstract: Fermions in (anti) de Sitter gravity theory in four dimensions are considered. Especially we propose new fermion actions to derive a Weyl or Majorana fermion action if we break the AdS (dS) group to the Lorentz group in curved spacetime.
